安装nodejs, npm(先不用更换apt源)

sudo apt update

sudo apt install nodejs npm


设定npm代理

sudo npm config set proxy http://USERNAME:PASSWORD@SERVER:PORT/ --global

sudo npm config set https-proxy http://USERNAME:PASSWORD@SERVER:PORT/ --global

sudo npm install -g --unsafe-perm node-red


参考：
https://yq.aliyun.com/articles/760437
https://blog.csdn.net/yanzi1225627/article/details/80247758
